      "id": "PopularPost42890",
      "post_content": "One of the best cards in the game, and an omnipresent addition to any deck running black. [Doom blade](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doom blade) will hit more types, but Terror cancels regeneration so they are equivalent.\n  \n   \nAbout the only spell that beats this guy is [terminate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=terminate) but for mono-black terror is still the best.\n  \n   \n4.5/5\n  ",
