      "id": "PopularPost86515",
      "post_content": "I have a question. This seems to be the only printed version of Terror where it is worded \"cannot *target* black or artifact creatures\", whereas all the other versions say \"destroy target non-black/non-artifact creature\". Now what if a [Horobi, Death's Wail](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Horobi, Death's Wail) is in play and you attempt to *target* a black creature with a Terror. Of course the Terror itself will not kill the creature, but with Horobi in play, any creature that becomes the target of a spell is destroyed... so can you *target* a black or artifact creature with Terror? And because of Horobi's ability it will be destroyed?",
      "posted_by": "warlockwar",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost86515\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">I have a question. This seems to be the only printed version of Terror where it is worded \"cannot <i>target</i> black or artifact creatures\", whereas all the other versions say \"destroy target non-black/non-artifact creature\". Now what if a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Horobi, Death's Wail\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Horobi, Death's Wail\">Horobi, Death's Wail</a> is in play and you attempt to <i>target</i> a black creature with a Terror. Of course the Terror itself will not kill the creature, but with Horobi in play, any creature that becomes the target of a spell is destroyed... so can you <i>target</i> a black or artifact creature with Terror? And because of Horobi's ability it will be destroyed?</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '86515'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy40259\">warlockwar</span>\r\n                                (7/10/2010 9:36:39 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"star