    {
      "id": "PopularPost363489",
      "post_content": "This card and this art are Magic icons. This had to be one of the most-played and most-recognizable cards of its time. I love the art. It truly captures the feel of this card and explains how sheer *terror* can actually kill a creature. And I love that it gives no hint at what is causing the fear because it is only in the victim's mind. Even the background is an utter void as everything fades out of consciousness until all that is left is the indescribable panic that completely overwhelms the nervous system.  \n  \nOh yeah, and a great card that goes in every black deck, blah, blah, blah... powerful instant-speed removal, yadda, yadda, yadda... ",
      "posted_by": "The_Riddle_of_Steel",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost363489\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">This card and this art are Magic icons. This had to be one of the most-played and most-recognizable cards of its time. I love the art. It truly captures the feel of this card and explains how sheer <i>terror</i> can actually kill a creature. And I love that it gives no hint at what is causing the fear because it is only in the victim's mind. Even the background is an utter void as everything fades out of consciousness until all that is left is the indescribable panic that completely overwhelms the nervous system.<br/><br/>Oh yeah, and a great card that goes in every black deck, blah, blah, blah... powerful instant-speed removal, yadda, yadda, yadda... </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '363489'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy105866\">The_Riddle_of_Steel</span>\r\n                                (2/13/2014 5:34:38 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubCo